media:group.media:title: 999 | Hololive Animation
media:group.media:description:
999 is an animatic film in which Ame tries to save Ina from The Ancient Ones.

Phew, this series took a while! I've been trying to blur the line between film and painting, and this is probably the farthest I have gone with it. 
Keep an eye out for the next series! 

Made with Photoshop, Blender, and Sony Vegas. 
Various sounds from Freesound.org
Music: Dova Syndrome - Beyond Redemption
